        <li>MSc (Hons) Data Science (Distinction) (Oct 2019 - Sep 2020)</li>
        <li>BSc (Hons) Computer Science (First) (Oct 2016 - June 2019)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="py-4">
      <h2
        class="font-bold text-text-heading text-xl md:text-2xl py-2 overflow-hidden"
      >
