        <li class="mb-2">
          NuPhy Air 75 low-profile mechanical keyboard (first choice)
        </li>
        <li class="mb-2">IQUNIX L80 mechnical keyboard (second choice)</li>
        <li class="mb-2">Logitech MX Master 3 mouse</li>
        <li class="mb-2">iPhone 14 Pro Max</li>
        <li class="mb-2">Apple Watch Series 6 (for general smartwatch use)</li>
